\name{melonmundiShinyUI-package}
\alias{melonmundiShinyUI}
\alias{melonmundiShinyUI-package}
\title{Shared Theme and UI Helpers for MelonMundi Shiny Apps}
\description{
Internal package that centralizes the shared MelonMundi Shiny theme and
reusable UI helpers used across product applications.
}
\details{
The package exposes a shared CSS dependency through \code{mm_use_theme()} and
small composable helpers for recurring surfaces such as cards, warnings,
status lines, steps and footers.
}
\seealso{
\code{\link{mm_use_theme}},
